Primary parameter values

Source: R/PM_model.R
PM_pri.Rd

Define primary model parameter object. This is used internally by the PM_model class.

Public fields

min

Minimum value of the range.

max

Maximum value of the range.

mean

Mean value of the range, calculated as (min + max) / 2.

sd

Standard deviation of the range, calculated as (max - min) / 6.

Methods

  • PM_pri$new()

  • PM_pri$print()
